s!','clarotm').'</em></p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:columns --><div class="wp-block-columns"><!-- wp:column {"width":"65%"} --><div class="wp-block-column" style="flex-basis:65%"><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>'.esc_html__('As I watched, the planet seemed to grow larger and smaller and to advance and recede, but that was simply that my eye was tired. Forty millions of miles it was from us — more than forty millions of miles of void. Few people realize the immensity of vacancy in which the dust of the material universe swims.','clarotm').'</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --></div><!-- /wp:column --><!-- wp:column {"width":"5%"} --><div class="wp-block-column" style="flex-basis:5%"></div><!-- /wp:column --><!-- wp:column {"width":"30%"} --><div class="wp-block-column" style="flex-basis:30%"><!-- wp:list --><ul><li>'.esc_html__('Towels','clarotm').'</li><li>'.esc_html__('Camera','clarotm').'</li><li>'.esc_html__('Water Bottle','clarotm').'</li><li>'.esc_html__('Swimsuit','clarotm').'</li><li>'.esc_html__('Snacks','clarotm').'</li></ul><!-- /wp:list --></div><!-- /wp:column --></div><!-- /wp:columns -->',));}